Description: Comprehensive Git workflow management CLI tool
 GitFlow Studio is a powerful command-line interface for Git workflow management
 that provides advanced features for developers and teams.
 .
 Features include:
  * Complete Git operations (status, log, branches, commits, push/pull)
  * Advanced Git operations (cherry-pick, revert, rebase, squash)
  * GitFlow workflow support (feature/release branches)
  * GitHub integration (OAuth, repositories, pull requests, notifications)
  * Stash and tag management
  * Repository analytics and statistics
  * Interactive CLI mode with rich formatting
  * Plugin system for extensibility
  * Repository discovery and management
  * Branch visualization and health metrics
 .
 This tool is designed for developers who want a comprehensive Git workflow
 solution with modern CLI interface and GitHub integration capabilities. 